THE "TAILLIGHT" OPEN SOURCE LICENSE

1. FREEDOM OF THE ROAD: Use this here code however you want. Copy it, swap it, paint it a different color, or try to sell it for a cold one. I don't care. It's yours now.

2. THE TAILLIGHT QUARANTEE: This here software is guaranteed to work right up until you can't see my taillights no more. Once I'm out of the driveway, you're on your own, hoss.

3. "AS-IS" (AS IN, AS IT IS): It's provided "AS-IS". That means if it works, hallelujah. If it don't, well, that's just the way the cookie crumbles. If it blows up your rig, starts a fire in the barn, or makes your dog run away, that ain't my problem.

4. NO BACK-TALKIN': By usin' this code, you're agreein' that if somethin' goes sideways, you won't come lookin' for me or my kin. No lawyers, no lawsuits, no fussin'. 

5. IF IT BREAKS, YOU BOUGHT BOTH HALVES: I ain't liable for nothin'. If you lose your data, your lunch, or your mind usin' this stuff, that's a "you" problem.

Now git to work and make somethin' cool.
